  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 400f",
    "rinse the quinoa and cook according to package instructions",
    "cut the mixed vegetables into bite-sized pieces",
    "brush the tofu with olive oil and season with black pepper",
    "grill the tofu on a binchotan-charcoal grill until crispy",
    "toss the mixed vegetables with olive oil, garlic, and ginger, and roast in the oven for 15-20 minutes",
    "in a small bowl, whisk together fish sauce, lime juice, and sugar, and set aside",
    "to assemble the bowls, divide the cooked quinoa among four bowls, top with roasted vegetables, grilled tofu, and a sprinkle of toasted sesame seeds"
